Description: Provides an R client to the TaxRef API
  <https://taxref.mnhn.fr/taxref-web/api/doc>, the French Taxonomical Reference
  Database which indexes names of species with unique identifiers as well as
  conservation statuses, biological interactions and taxonomic relationships.
